@startuml
title E-Uprava - Use Case Dijagram

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam linetype ortho

actor "Neregistrovani\nkorisnik" as Gost
actor "Korisnik" as Korisnik
actor "Admin" as Admin

rectangle "E-Uprava - Sistem" {

  package "Autentifikacija" {
    usecase "Registracija" as UC_Register
    usecase "Login" as UC_Login
    usecase "Logout" as UC_Logout
    usecase "Pregled profila" as UC_Profile
  }

  package "Vrtić" {
    usecase "Pregled vrtića" as UC_Vrtici
    usecase "Pretraga i filtriranje" as UC_Filter
    usecase "Sortiranje vrtića" as UC_Sort
    usecase "Poređenje vrtića" as UC_Compare
    usecase "Pregled detalja vrtića" as UC_Details

    usecase "Slanje zahteva za upis" as UC_Enroll
    usecase "Pregled mojih zahteva" as UC_MyEnroll
    usecase "Ocenjivanje vrtića" as UC_Rate

    usecase "Upravljanje vrtićima" as UC_Manage
    usecase "Dodavanje vrtića" as UC_Create
    usecase "Izmena vrtića" as UC_Update
    usecase "Brisanje vrtića" as UC_Delete

    usecase "Obrada zahteva za upis" as UC_Requests
    usecase "Pregled svih zahteva" as UC_AllRequests
    usecase "Odobravanje zahteva" as UC_Approve
    usecase "Odbijanje zahteva" as UC_Reject
  }

  package "Otvoreni podaci" {
    usecase "Pregled otvorenih podataka" as UC_OpenData
    usecase "Pregled statistike" as UC_Stats
    usecase "Kritično popunjeni vrtići" as UC_Critical
    usecase "Najbolje opštine" as UC_Ranking
    usecase "Pokrivenost po opštini" as UC_Coverage
    usecase "Projekcija potreba" as UC_Projection
    usecase "PDF izveštaj po opštini" as UC_PDF
    usecase "Preuzimanje JSON podataka" as UC_JSON
  }
}

Gost --> UC_Register
Gost --> UC_Login
Gost --> UC_Vrtici
Gost --> UC_OpenData

Korisnik --> UC_Logout
Korisnik --> UC_Profile
Korisnik --> UC_Vrtici
Korisnik --> UC_OpenData
Korisnik --> UC_Enroll
Korisnik --> UC_MyEnroll
Korisnik --> UC_Rate

Admin --> UC_Logout
Admin --> UC_Profile
Admin --> UC_Vrtici
Admin --> UC_OpenData
Admin --> UC_Manage
Admin --> UC_Requests

UC_Vrtici ..> UC_Filter : <<include>>
UC_Vrtici ..> UC_Sort : <<include>>
UC_Vrtici ..> UC_Compare : <<extend>>
UC_Vrtici ..> UC_Details : <<include>>

UC_Manage ..> UC_Create : <<include>>
UC_Manage ..> UC_Update : <<include>>
UC_Manage ..> UC_Delete : <<include>>

UC_Requests ..> UC_AllRequests : <<include>>
UC_Requests ..> UC_Approve : <<include>>
UC_Requests ..> UC_Reject : <<include>>

UC_OpenData ..> UC_Stats : <<include>>
UC_OpenData ..> UC_Critical : <<include>>
UC_OpenData ..> UC_Ranking : <<include>>
UC_OpenData ..> UC_Coverage : <<include>>
UC_OpenData ..> UC_Projection : <<include>>
UC_OpenData ..> UC_PDF : <<extend>>
UC_OpenData ..> UC_JSON : <<extend>>

Gost -[hidden]down- Korisnik
Korisnik -[hidden]down- Admin

note right of Admin
Admin upravlja samo
svojim vrtićima i
obrađuje zahteve za
svoje vrtiće.
end note

@enduml
